  "body": "For sanity we want to standardise extra-consensus various concepts related to deposits. The suggestion is to add those standards in this repo, similar to the [networking standards](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/tree/dev/specs/networking). @CarlBeek is doing some experimentation in [this repo](https://github.com/CarlBeek/eth2.0-deposit-tooling).\r\n\r\n- [x] 0. **rewrite BLS spec**: Follow new standards (see  [here](https://github.com/cfrg/draft-irtf-cfrg-hash-to-curve) and [here](https://github.com/cfrg/draft-irtf-cfrg-bls-signature)).\r\n- [ ] 1. **checksums**: see #1183\r\n- [ ] 2. **HD wallets**: see https://github.com/CarlBeek/eth2.0-deposit-tooling\r\n- [ ] 3. **key store**: see https://github.com/CarlBeek/eth2.0-deposit-tooling\r\n- [ ] 4. **quantum-secure backups**: see #1342\r\n",
